{"tid":1005814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【5億亂咁使】醫管局聘「炒散」填數    連游游都去做炒散護士！","createTime":"2019-02-02T13:00:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T16:19:54.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6ea6e81d99ed18cb22ae879151803c813f5d6bbc","tid":1005814,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T13:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/SK2d0qxt/NURSE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FSK2d0qxt%2FNURSE.jpg&h=070b3067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n流感高峯，公立醫院病房不勝負荷，特首林鄭月娥日前公佈，會如去年一樣撥款5億元予醫管局應付需求，而醫管局就透過中介公司聘請「炒散」兼職護士，聲稱有助解決燃眉之急。不過有前線護士向《蘋果》爆料，中介制度根本不能發揮效用，因為部份中介護士甚至不懂插喉打針，功能僅如「雜務阿姐」的病房助理。醫管局總護理行政經理潘恩榮承認，在招聘時只需持有護士執照，直言「有人就盡量請返嚟用」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190131/large/1548925948_6c8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190131%2Flarge%2F1548925948_6c8e.jpg&h=aeb2268b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中介護士做病房助理工作<br />\n不過，有前線護士爆料指，中介護士原來「只係客串幾日就消失」，而且對病房日常運作毫不熟悉，「派藥、打針、上水（吊鹽水），佢哋都唔會做到，要佢哋幫手拆條鹽水過床，（中介護士）都係蹺埋對手等我哋自己搞」，最終中介護士時薪雖比全職及兼職護士高，但只是負責餵飯、量血壓、驗血糖等，在全職護士眼中「好簡單，一個護士學生都可以做到嘅嘢」，更形容中介護士工作如處理雜務的病房助理。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，醫院硬件亦對中介護士欠缺支援，中介護士因為不能登入醫院電腦系統，以致未能協助派藥。中介護士完成部份病房工作後，更要全職護士協助「入機」輸入相關資料至系統中，變相與「自己做」無異。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2393503/org/a506ac825fdb3d2b29cd19b409833bb3.jpg/Glbk3oHDpXS8NFnGvv5PAdhWvqjqzcEalRy9lJUcvZQ?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2393503%2Forg%2Fa506ac825fdb3d2b29cd19b409833bb3.jpg%2FGlbk3oHDpXS8NFnGvv5PAdhWvqjqzcEalRy9lJUcvZQ%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=c7e25f62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n議員批只為跑數漠視前線<br />\n衞生服務界立法會議員李國麟指，中介護士未能發揮最大效用，有機會是因為中介護士過去在私人市場執業，擔任私家看護、或是在私家醫院工作，「以前一個對一個（病人）、或者一個對兩個，但依家一下子要照顧十個病人」，認為中介護士即使有其專業資格，亦會無所適從。"},{"pid":"2ca867fc1dae50c4ada3f6a9ef60fba3dfe5be0d","tid":1005814,"uid":4780,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T13:06:01.000Z","msg":"接nurse job<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係護士丫豬丫狗都做得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc4b77bfa585853c8fe140b3865750350ba7448","tid":1005814,"uid":389,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ca867fc1dae50c4ada3f6a9ef60fba3dfe5be0d","tid":1005814,"uid":4780,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T13:06:01.000Z","msg":"接nurse job<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係護士丫豬丫狗都做得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T13:08:08.000Z","msg":"佢話晒EN<br />\n又平又好用<br />\n醫生肉便器"},{"pid":"e44aae178c60bb683f775e55e50a3dc1a01d1048","tid":1005814,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T13:08:14.000Z","msg":"自食其果"},{"pid":"a149d2a5235bb3ce2ae6d3ae4841c9955c9ab052","tid":1005814,"uid":60344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T13:09:30.000Z","msg":"應該可以叫啲學生幫手"},{"pid":"b7d7215cddc6e5e89f364eef217bf0b749990650","tid":1005814,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ca867fc1dae50c4ada3f6a9ef60fba3dfe5be0d","tid":1005814,"uid":4780,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T13:06:01.000Z","msg":"接nurse job<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係護士丫豬丫狗都做得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T13:09:59.000Z","msg":"游游好似真係有牌<br />\n<br />\n做成點就唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\